      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。基础设施层作为Phase 0先启动，那具体包含哪些模块？ConfigModule、DatabaseModule这些都要放进去吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Phase 0",
