        "DatabaseModule"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Phase 0放ConfigModule、DatabaseModule和NotificationModule这三个基础设施模块。它们分别对接教育系统的ContentCDN、StudentDB和GradeSync。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Phase 0",
        "ConfigModule",
        "DatabaseModule",
        "NotificationModule",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，基础设施部分已经画好了。接下来Domain层怎么划分？是放在一个Phase还是再细分？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Domain"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Domain层我考虑分成Phase 1和Phase 2。Phase 1启动PaymentModule、ProductModule和UserModule，Phase 2再启动OrderModule。因为下单流程依赖前面几个模块就绪。",
      "elements_involved": [
